Description:
Near the farm, you come across a burned field and a burning house.

In front of the house there is a fire imp causing fires next to some burning cornies.

Even half burned, the house may contain something valuable, but you'll have to deal with the fire imp and cornies first.
DescriptionAction: You can deal with the imp and investigate the house or ignore him.
